# Keep these files
!README.md
!QUICKSTART.md
!DEPLOYMENT.md
!CHANGELOG.md
!FINAL_SUMMARY.md
!VERIFICATION.md
!INDEX.md
!COMPLETION_REPORT.md
!main.py
!config.py
!requirements.txt
!keywords.txt
!run.py
!setup_check.py
!.gitignore

# Important: Never commit real credentials
# Before committing, verify:
# 1. config.py has example credentials (not real ones)
# 2. No .log files committed
# 3. No __pycache__ directories
# 4. No venv folders
